{"id":101,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":101,"title":"Acts 6","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 6"],[".studySummary",["i","The Apostles choose seven to assist them—Stephen is tried before the council."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.1","order":"03.07.006.12452"},["b","1"],"And in those days, when the number of the disciples was multiplied, there arose a murmuring of the Grecians against the Hebrews, because their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"widows"],"were",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"neglected"],"in the daily",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"ministration"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.2","order":"03.07.006.12453"},["b","2"],"Then the twelve called the multitude of the disciples",["i","unto them,"],"and said, It is not reason that we should leave the word of God, and serve tables."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.3","order":"03.07.006.12454"},["b","3"],"Wherefore, brethren, look ye out among you seven men of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"honest"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"report"],", full of the Holy Ghost and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"wisdom"],", whom we may appoint over this",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_3d"},"business"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.4","order":"03.07.006.12455"},["b","4"],"But we will give ourselves continually to prayer, and to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"ministry"],"of the word."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.5","order":"03.07.006.12456"},["b","5"],"¶And the saying pleased the whole multitude: and they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"chose"],"Stephen, a man full of faith and of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Holy Ghost"],", and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"Philip"],", and Prochorus, and Nicanor, and Timon, and Parmenas, and Nicolas a proselyte of Antioch:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.6","order":"03.07.006.12457"},["b","6"],"Whom they set before the apostles: and when they had prayed, they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"laid"],["i","their"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"hands"],"on them."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.7","order":"03.07.006.12458"},["b","7"],"And the word of God increased; and the number of the disciples multiplied in Jerusalem greatly; and a great company of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"priests"],"were obedient to the faith."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.8","order":"03.07.006.12459"},["b","8"],"And Stephen, full of faith and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"power"],", did great wonders and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"miracles"],"among the people."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.9","order":"03.07.006.12460"},["b","9"],"¶Then there arose certain of the synagogue, which is called",["i","the synagogue"],"of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Libertines"],", and Cyrenians, and Alexandrians, and of them of Cilicia and of Asia,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"disputing"],"with Stephen."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.10","order":"03.07.006.12461"},["b","10"],"And they were not able to resist the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"wisdom"],"and the spirit by which he spake."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.11","order":"03.07.006.12462"},["b","11"],"Then they suborned men, which said, We have heard him speak",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"blasphemous"],"words against Moses, and",["i","against"],"God."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.12","order":"03.07.006.12463"},["b","12"],"And they stirred up the people, and the elders, and the scribes, and came upon",["i","him,"],"and caught him, and brought",["i","him"],"to the council,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.13","order":"03.07.006.12464"},["b","13"],"And set up",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"false witnesses"],", which said, This man ceaseth not to speak blasphemous words against this holy place, and the law:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.14","order":"03.07.006.12465"},["b","14"],"For we have heard him say, that this Jesus of Nazareth shall destroy this place, and shall change the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"customs"],"which Moses delivered us."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.15","order":"03.07.006.12466"},["b","15"],"And all that sat in the council, looking steadfastly on him, saw his face as it had been the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"face"],"of an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"angel"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.1a","order":"03.07.006.12467"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/widows"},"TG Widows"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.1b","order":"03.07.006.12469"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apathy"},"TG Apathy"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/welfare"},"Welfare"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.1c","order":"03.07.006.12471"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/4.35"},"Acts 4:35"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.3a","order":"03.07.006.12473"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-qualifying-for"},"Priesthood, Qualifying for"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.3b","order":"03.07.006.12475"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/3.7"},"1 Tim. 3:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.3c","order":"03.07.006.12477"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.3d","order":"03.07.006.12479"},["b","3d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.68.14,68"},"D&C 107:68 (14, 68)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.4a","order":"03.07.006.12481"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/16.15.15-19"},"Mark 16:15 (15–19)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.8"},"D&C 107:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.5a","order":"03.07.006.12483"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/called-of-god"},"TG Called of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.5b","order":"03.07.006.12485"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-gifts-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Gifts of"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.5c","order":"03.07.006.12487"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.8"},"Acts 21:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.6a","order":"03.07.006.12489"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church-organization"},"TG Church Organization"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of"},"Hands, Laying on of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood"},"Priesthood"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-authority"},"Priesthood, Authority"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.6b","order":"03.07.006.12491"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/setting-apart"},"TG Setting Apart"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.7a","order":"03.07.006.12493"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.42"},"John 12:42"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priest-aaronic-priesthood"},"TG Priest, Aaronic Priesthood"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bd/priests"},"BD Priests"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.8a","order":"03.07.006.12495"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-power-of"},"TG Priesthood, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.8b","order":"03.07.006.12497"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/miracle"},"TG Miracle"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.9a","order":"03.07.006.12499"},["b","9a"],["span.small","GR"],"Freed-men."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.9b","order":"03.07.006.12501"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disputations"},"TG Disputations"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.10a","order":"03.07.006.12503"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.17"},"Isa. 54:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.15"},"Luke 21:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/100.5.5-6"},"D&C 100:5 (5–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.11a","order":"03.07.006.12505"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blaspheme"},"TG Blaspheme"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.13a","order":"03.07.006.12507"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/slander"},"TG Slander"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.14a","order":"03.07.006.12509"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.21"},"Acts 21:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.15a","order":"03.07.006.12511"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.36"},"Hel. 5:36"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/6.15b","order":"03.07.006.12513"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/angels"},"TG Angels"],"."]]}
